textAfterTable: The clean, lovely lines of these frames will adorn any artwork that you may have to frame. They accept stretched canvas, wood panels, art boards and even mounted and matted artwork. Made to the most demanding standards, Ambiance Gallery Deep wood Frames feature unbreakable acrylic glazing and rigid MDF wood panel backing. Each frame has a 7/8" face with a crisp clean line, and the 1.5" depth allows you to frame almost any standard sized canvas, too. Select from seven lovely finishes including: Natural, Black, Mahogany, Cherry, Walnut, White Wash and pure White. Simply put, there is not a better value in framing on the planet! Sold individually or in boxes of 8; minimum purchase of 4 assorted frames required. SAFE AND SECURE
